HEADWORD: Rough-grained
<hw>Rough"-grained</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having a rough
grain or fiber; hence, figuratively, having coarse traits of character;
not polished; brisque.</def>⟦br⟧
